### Test 1 - Invalid signature (expect 401)
POST http://localhost:8005/webhook/jira
Content-Type: application/json
X-Hub-Signature: sha256=invalid

{
  "webhookEvent": "jira:issue_created",
  "issue": {
    "key": "B1-1001",
    "fields": {
      "project": { "key": "B1" }
    }
  }
}

